msgstr "1\. Basic Examples"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.md:7
msgid "1.1 受限玻尔兹曼机（RBM）"
msgstr "1.1 Restricted Boltzmann Machine (RBM)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.md:9
msgid ""
"以下示例展示了如何使用 `RestrictedBoltzmannMachine` 类进行基本的模型训练。 "
"可以定义可见节点、隐藏节点的个数，以及自定义二次项和一次项的初始化。"
msgstr ""
"The snippet below shows basic training with the "
"``RestrictedBoltzmannMachine`` class. You can set the number of visible "
"and hidden units and optionally supply custom initial values for the "
"quadratic and linear terms."

